# Antigravity Extractor Data Files

Folder ini menyimpan data hasil antigravity extractor:
- name analyzer
- Discord PFP + name ritual extractor

## File Structure

```
extracted-data/
├── antigravity-name-analyzer.json      # Data analisis nama
├── antigravity-ritual-extractor.json   # Data Discord Ritual
└── antigravity-status.json             # Status extraction progress
```

## Cara Update

```bash
# Setelah run antigravity extractor
git add extracted-data/antigravity-*.json
git commit -m "update: antigravity data [timestamp]"
git push origin main
```

## Cara Pull di PC Lain

```bash
git pull origin main
# Data siap digunakan
```
